<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.99.90114.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Echinolaophonte musa sp. nov. female. A. Antennule; B. Distal segment of antennule; C. Antenna; arrow pointing to abexopodal seta; Roman numerals labelling subapical, Arabian numerals labelling apical elements; D. Mandible; E. Maxillule; F. Maxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/827554" ;
